  <brief_title>ACVBP Followed by ASCT in Patients With BCL-2 Positive Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Study of ACVBP Followed by Autologous Stem Cell Transplantation in Case of BCL-2 Overexpression in Non Previously Treated Patients Aged 60 Years or Less With Low-Intermediate Risk Diffuse Large B-Cell Lymphoma</official_title>
