  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the study is to evaluate the efficacy of ASCT as consolidation in
      case of bcl-2 overexpression in non previously treated patients aged 60 years or less with
      low-intermediate risk diffuse large B-cell lymphoma who responded to ACVBP regimen. Our goal
      is to obtain a 15% increase of event-free survival at 2 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
